Controls for dime - OGRE
This is a temporary file, when dime is more advanced the controls will be defined via the configuration service.

MOUSE: look around when not in game GUI mode
		point & click when in game GUI mode

W: walk forward
S: walk backwards
A: sidestep left
D: sidestep right

O: camera yaw
P: camera yaw
I: camera pitch
K: camera pitch

F: toggle debug GUI on / off
Y: toggle wireframe mode
H: toggle game GUI on / off

ESC: quit game
